        <updateDate>2021-09-14T17:48:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Restoring Military Focus Act</strong></p> <p>This bill eliminates the position of Chief Diversity Officer within the Department of Defense (DOD). Additionally, the bill prohibits federal funds from being used to establish a position similar to that of Chief Diversity Officer or Senior Advisor for Diversity and Inclusion within DOD.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
